Pamela Reed https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pamela_Reed 0 Pamela Reed (born April 2, 1949) is an American actress. She is known for playing Arnold Schwarzenegger's hypoglycemic police partner in the 1990 movie Kindergarten Cop and as the matriarch Gail Green in Jericho. She appeared as Marlene Griggs-Knope on the NBC sitcom Parks and Recreation. Pamela_Reed ( born April_2_,_1949 ) is an_American_actress .
